New_LLAMA_ZS_HDFS_2:
10.251.42.246:50010:Got exception while serving blk_<*> to <*>:<*>


### Note:
You can assume the log message is always in the same format, and the template always consists of a series of placeholders, separated by a space.


### Python Solution
```python
def parse_log(log):
    return log.replace("blk_", "<*>").replace(":", "<*>")
```

### Java Solution
```java
public String parseLog(String log) {
    return log.replace("blk_", "<*>").replace(":", "<*>");
}
``

